remove_criminal

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remove_criminal -  This method removes a player from the criminals array
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int remove_criminal(string place_name,
mixed player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^place_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the place to clear the player's crime ledger
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the name or object of the player to remove
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if successfully removed, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/crime_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method removes a player from the criminals array
.EP

